quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,Have you seen the one who denies the Day of Judgment
  107,2,It is he who drives away the orphan (harshly)
  107,3,and don’t encourage the feeding of the poor
  107,4,So woe to those who perform prayers (hypocrites)
  107,5,but are heedless of their prayer
  107,6,those who do good deeds only to be seen
  107,7,and they refuge (to share) small kindnesses